<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-danger"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p> I've always loved to learn, and one of my favorite things to study has been languages. I started out in elementary with Spanish, one I sadly did not continue but it gave me my first intro into the language world. This was followed by Japanese which gave me a love for learning about not just language but culture. Finally my language skills evolved with French and Chinese, including two wonderful opportunities that landed me in China for two summers in a row.  </p>
        <p>To me coding is just another set of languages to learn. It's a culture within itself that I am eager to continue learning and developing.</p>
       
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-danger"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-danger"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Complete Weddings--Photobooth Operator
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Impact China-- Teacher
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Utah State University
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
             Viewmont High School
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>